<p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  You've just experienced the tool that Swindon Borough Council built to slash translation
  costs by 99.96% and make Easy Read accessible to every council. In this walkthrough, you've seen
  what typically requires months of procurement and vendor negotiations.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you've learned</h2>

<div class="ndx-takeaway-grid">
  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Document Translation
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Translate documents into 75+ languages using Amazon Translate. From £160 per document
      to £0.07. From 19 days to 14 minutes.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: 99.96% cost reduction, near-instant turnaround
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Easy Read
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Convert complex documents to Easy Read format using Amazon Bedrock. Co-created with
      people with learning disabilities to ensure genuine accessibility.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: From £120/page to ~1p/page, accessible in minutes not weeks
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Open Source
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Built as an AWS Sample, open source and free to deploy. No vendor lock-in,
      no licensing fees. Any council can use it today.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Zero cost to adopt, community-supported
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Built by Local Gov
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Pioneered by Swindon Borough Council's Emerging Technology team. Now adopted
      by Edinburgh, Newport, Southampton, West Berkshire, and councils in France.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Proven in production, designed for council needs
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

